---
title: Mushroom Po’boys & Boardwalk Fries with Slaw, Pickles & Spicy Remoulade
description: These po’boys are an embarrassment of riches. They star mushrooms coated in a crispy tempura batter that’s kicked up with Old Bay seasoning. A creamy, tangy slaw makes for a quick topping while pickles and a zippy sauce are reminiscent of remoulade. Layer everything on toasty baguettes and you’ve got a combo that’ll transport you to NOLA. Want fries with that? Yeah, you do! The oven-baked potato wedges sprinkled with more Old Bay will make you feel like a million bucks.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mushroom-poboys-boardwalk-fries-2714f05f.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/mushroom-poboys-boardwalk-fries-61c1e6c7269d6279c50cd32a-ee70c454.pdf
